{"tid":55153,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[天水圍巴絲入] 新北江真係好垃圾","createTime":"2016-12-26T07:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T18:37:54.000Z","uid":53597,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61687ac41b7058c4af8c1724bf63e39cbe2ff95f","tid":55153,"uid":53597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫襯過新北江呢間黑店<br />\n<br />\n去新北江食野不嬲都冇好大期望<br />\n先唔講呢間野有幾難食<br />\n今次真係比個老闆娘吹漲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1TDT6C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1TDT6C.jpg&h=92fa1d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說25號晏晝去左新北江冰山之國<br />\n買個撈麵<br />\n撈完比我之後 我用支牙籤督下<br />\n嘩屌 堆海帶結冰嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小姐你有冇撈過架 成舊結哂冰叫人點食<br />\n你估自己真係係冰山開鋪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y32N65z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY32N65z.jpg&h=26a7612c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就行過去拎起舊海帶比佢睇 叫佢換番包海帶比我<br />\n然後佢同我講<br />\n&quot;如果你舊野食唔到,可以去個邊個垃圾桶掉左佢&quot;<br />\n下 做生意做撚到你咁仆街都得嘅<br />\n賣啲結冰撈唔好嘅野出黎 然後叫買左嘅人扔左佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我之後話, 你賣啲野咁嘅野出去<br />\n你叫人點食<br />\n又唔肯換比人<br />\n有冇搞錯<br />\n<br />\n然後個老闆娘爆seed 話因爲包野係我自己拎自己揀 結左冰唔關佢事<br />\n咁世界級嘅答法 我真係o撚哂嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後來 隔離有個岩岩買左撈麵嘅阿姨睇唔過眼<br />\n叫佢換番比人 佢先肯換番包餸比我<br />\n<br />\n好耐冇食野食到咁嬲<br />\n奉勸大家唔好幫襯呢間無良食店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f675ce4e1e1e81bad6474edf4b881e54cfcab6aa","tid":55153,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T07:29:40.000Z","msg":"咁真係你自己揀架喎<br />\n你拎上手時感覺唔到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />